<div id="WelcomeDiv" style="font-size:160%;padding:0.1em 0;margin:0.2em 0 -0.5em"><span class="MainTopText"><a href="/MarioWiki:Introduction" title="MarioWiki:Introduction">Welcome to the <b>Super Mario Wiki</b>!</a></span></div>
<div id="WithText" class="MainTopText">with <a href="/Special:Statistics" title="Special:Statistics">35,846</a> <a href="/Special:AllPages" title="Special:AllPages">articles</a> covering <i><a href="/Super_Mario_(franchise)" title="Super Mario (franchise)">Super Mario</a></i> and <a href="/MarioWiki:Coverage" title="MarioWiki:Coverage">more</a></div>
