<tr>
<td>
<div style="padding:3px 8px 2px">
<div><div class="floatleft"><a href="/MarioWiki:Mushroom_World_Encyclopedia" title="Mushroom World Encyclopedia"><img alt="Mushroom World Encyclopedia" src="https://mario.wiki.gallery/images/thumb/1/12/Mushroom_world_encyclopedia.png/100px-Mushroom_world_encyclopedia.png" decoding="async" loading="lazy" width="100" height="85" class="invert-dark" srcset="https://mario.wiki.gallery/images/thumb/1/12/Mushroom_world_encyclopedia.png/150px-Mushroom_world_encyclopedia.png 1.5x, https://mario.wiki.gallery/images/1/12/Mushroom_world_encyclopedia.png 2x" data-file-width="200" data-file-height="169" /></a></div> The <b><a href="/MarioWiki:Mushroom_World_Encyclopedia" title="MarioWiki:Mushroom World Encyclopedia">Mushroom World Encyclopedia</a></b> is a multilingual and open-content project which includes the independent encyclopedias covering the <i><a href="/Super_Mario_(franchise)" title="Super Mario (franchise)">Super Mario</a></i> franchise from different areas of the world.
<div style="text-align:center;margin-top:9px"><a class="mw-selflink selflink">English</a> | <a href="https://wikimario.fr/Wiki_Mario" class="extiw" title="fr:Wiki Mario">French</a> | <a href="https://mariowiki.net/wiki/MarioWiki:Hauptseite" class="extiw" title="de:MarioWiki:Hauptseite">German</a> | <a href="https://www.mariowiki.it/Pagina_principale" class="extiw" title="it:Pagina principale">Italian</a></div></div>
</div>
